Framework is a way to organize your code
It should be 
	a.reusable
	b.scalable ( used for any kind of applications )
	c.Maintainable
	d.Understandable
	e.workable
Types of frameworks available
	a. Data driven - huge number of input data
	b. Keyword driven - enables non automation testers to write scripts.( excel sheets )
	c. Hybrid - combination of both data driven and keyword driven.